name: Dino Park: Free Jurassic Simulator in Wonder World
name_original: Dino Park: Free Jurassic Simulator in Wonder World
description:
The dinosaur world has gone mad! The T-Rex is not the strongest animal any more!

The Triceratops dinosaur has become wilder than ever and goes for the velociraptor!

Choose one of the available dinosaurs and avoid this apocalyptic jungle environment!

Be careful and do not crash against any other dinosaur fleeing the terror!

Enjoy this dinosaur game as much as other children do!

Show your Jurassic skills with wonderful graphics of the jungle!

Stay in touch with us for our future funny games!
